@redsunsoft so mainly were hoping for a code review in case there are some ways to improve perf. There is a lag loading that trace, it doesn't snap, but larger traces can be slower. It is all subjective I guess. I know larger traces are problematic (approaching 10k spans), but we don't have one here.

At the moment, the new UI is under zipkin-lens, so probably feedback there will end up with highest value.

At any rate an example setup for benchmarking added to help track down perf concerns would be good if you have integration ideas and/or instructions.
